ORANGE COUNTY DIGEST / LOCAL NEWS IN BRIEF: BREA; 
BREA BLVD. RENOVATION TO BE CELEBRATED TODAY 
Festivities to celebrate the renovation of Brea Boulevard south of Imperial 
Highway will begin today at 5 p.m. with a party and ribbon-cutting ceremony at 
633 S. Brea Blvd. 
The celebration will continue on Saturday from noon to 6:30 p.m. with a $10,000 
raffle and a chance to meet California Angels pitcher Bert Blyleven and former 
UCLA basketball star Ann Meyers. 
